outservice与下游服务的网络连接状况\n- 检查Redis集群的健康状态和资源使用情况\n- 监控ShippingService的资源使用率和错误率\n- 验证PaymentService是否也存在类似延迟问题", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "e1562aa2-335", "component": "cartservice-2", "reason": "pod_processes 指标变化导致 rrt_max 和 rrt 飙升，p99响应时间从12007ms增加到67892ms", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LoadMetrics(cartservice-2)", "observation": "pod_processes 指标变化，rrt_max 从5015ms增加到5644ms，p99从12007ms飙升到67892ms"}, {"step": 2, "action": "TraceAnalysis(e1562aa2-335)", "observation": "redis->cartservice 调用链中HMSET操作延迟飙升13.3倍，影响checkoutservice下游性能"}, {"step": 3, "action": "CheckNodePodMapping()", "observation": "cartservice-2 运行在aiops-k8s-08节点，该节点内存可用量异常增加22.13%"}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
